                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I play at Riches -- to appease</l>
                    <l>The Clamoring for Gold --</l>
                    <l>It kept me from a Thief, I think,</l>
                    <l>For often, overbold</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>With Want, and Opportunity --</l>
                    <l>I <app type="revision"><lem>might</lem><rdg>might</rdg></app>
could have done a Sin</l>
                    <l>And been Myself that <app type="revision"><lem>distant</lem><rdg>distant</rdg></app>
easy Thing</l>
                    <l>An independant Man --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>But often as my lot displays</l>
                    <l>Too hungry to be borne</l>
                    <l>I deem Myself what I would be --</l>
                    <l>And <app type="revision"><lem>so much</lem><rdg>so much</rdg></app>
novel Comforting</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>My Poverty and I derived --</l>
                    <l>We question if the Man --</l>
                    <l>Who own -- Esteem the Opulence --</l>
                    <l>As We -- Who never Can --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Should ever these exploring Hands</l>
                    <l>Chance Sovreign on a Mine --</l>
                    <l>Or in the long -- uneven term</l>
                    <l>To win, become <app type="revision"><lem>my</lem><rdg>my</rdg></app>
their turn --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l><app type="revision"><lem>'Tis</lem><rdg>&#x27;Tis</rdg></app>
How fitter <app type="revision"><lem>I shall he --</lem><rdg>I shall he --</rdg></app>
they will be -- for Want --</l>
                    <l>Enlightening so well --</l>
                    <l>I know not which, Desire, or <app type="revision"><lem>Right --</lem><rdg>Right --</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>sight</lem><rdg>sight</rdg></app>
Grant --</l>
                    <l>Be <app type="revision"><lem>chiefest</lem><rdg>chiefest</rdg></app>
<app type="revision"><lem>utmost</lem><rdg>utmost</rdg></app>
wholly beautiful --</l>
                </lg>
